Howards End;;81;;94;;PG;;Helen Schlegel falls for Paul Wilcox, but is rebuffed. Her sister Margaret becomes friends with his mother, who promises her the family house, Howards End. Unfortunately, after her death, the will disappears and it appears the inheritance will disappear. Until the widower, Henry Wilcox, becomes attracted to Margaret.;;Drama;;James Ivory;;1992;;Anthony Hopkins,Emma Thompson,Helena Bonham Carter,Vanessa Redgrave,James Wilby,Samuel West,Jemma Redgrave,Nicola Duffett,Prunella Scales,Susie Lindeman,Adrian Ross Magenty,Barbara Hicks;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/howards_end